           Type: attribute set of (string or signed integer or boolean or list
           of string)

           Default: { }

           Example:

               {
                 Create = "both";
                 CopyArrivalDate = "yes";
                 MaxMessages = 10000;
                 MaxSize = "1m";
               }

           Declared by:
               <home-manager/modules/programs/mbsync.nix>

       accounts.email.accounts.<name>.mbsync.groups.<name>.channels.<name>.farPattern
           IMAP4 patterns for which mailboxes on the remote mail server to
           sync. If ‘Patterns’ are specified, ‘farPattern’ is interpreted as a
           prefix which is not matched against the patterns, and is not
           affected by mailbox list overrides.

           If this is left as the default, then mbsync will default to the
           pattern ‘INBOX’.

           Type: string

           Default: ""

           Example: "[Gmail]/Sent Mail"

           Declared by:
               <home-manager/modules/programs/mbsync.nix>

